HEADWORD: Iridal
<hw>I"ri*dal</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>iris</ets>, <ets>iridis</ets>, rainbow. See <er>Iris</er>.]</ety>
